	<p pid="a.25.8/1">The previous Minister for Immigration and Asylum met representatives of Church Action against Poverty on <phrase class="date" code="2006-05-17">17 May</phrase> to discuss the support available to failed asylum seekers. He confirmed that options for providing assistance to failed asylum seekers&mdash;including the possibility of them taking paid work&mdash;were being kept under review.</p>
</reply>
