	<p pid="a.34.2/1">The current mainline rail contract is due to expire on <phrase class="date" code="">31 March 2007</phrase>. An advertisement for expressions of interest was placed in the <i>Official Journal of the European Union </i>and in the <i>Ministry of Defence Contracts Bulletin</i> on <phrase class="date" code="2006-06-08">8 June 2006</phrase>. The contract re-let process will be fully compliant with government procurement procedures.</p>
